#ROOM
Vnum     11200
Name     &OThe Gates of Orgrimmar&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand before the awe-inspiring, brutalist architecture of Orgrimmar.
Massive iron spikes and logs the size of houses form a heavily fortified
gate protecting the canyon within. The dry heat of Durotar bears down
mercilessly.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11201
Desc      The path leads under the massive iron spikes into the city.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11200 2 11200
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
  Reset E 1 11201 10 12
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11201
Name     &OThe Main Gateway&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You are walking through the thick, heavily defended tunnel that serves
as the only ground entrance to the Horde capital. Torches flicker against
the rough-hewn stone walls. The smell of dust, sweat, and forge fires
drifts from the north.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11202
Desc      The gateway opens up into the Valley of Strength.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11200
Desc      The blazing sun of Durotar waits outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11200 2 11201
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11202
Name     &OValley of Strength - South Walk&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The canyon opens up dramatically, revealing the Valley of Strength. The
ground is baked red earth. Enormous wooden structures with taut hide
roofs surround a central pillar of stone. The constant sound of drums
and hammering fills the air.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11203
Desc      The bustling central pillar of the Valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11201
Desc      The gateway leading out of the city.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11207 2 11202
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11203
Name     &OValley of Strength - Central Pillar&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand at the crossroads of the Valley of Strength, wrapping around
a massive natural pillar of red rock. Warriors, peons, and shaman
hurry past. To the west is the heavily guarded Bank, and to the east
lies the chaotic Auction House.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11208
Desc      The path winds northward.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11206
Desc      The entrance to the Orgrimmar Auction House.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11202
Desc      The path back toward the main gates.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11204
Desc      The heavily reinforced Orgrimmar Bank.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11204 3 11203
  Reset E 1 11208 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11204
Name     &OOrgrimmar Bank&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This structure is built directly into the canyon wall, reinforced with
thick iron plates and heavy wooden beams. Goblins and orcs alike manage
the immense wealth of the Horde here, keeping a highly suspicious eye
on anyone who lingers too long.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11203
Desc      The dusty central pillar of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    11205
Desc      A ramp leads down into the vaults.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11203 2 11204
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11205
Name     &OThe Bank Vaults&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     The air down here is cool and smells of oiled iron and gold dust. Rows
upon rows of heavy strongboxes are bolted to the solid stone floor. It
would take an army to break into this subterranean fortress.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    11204
Desc      The ramp leads up to the main banking floor.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11203 2 11205
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
Reset O 0 11206 1 11205
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11206
Name     &OOrgrimmar Auction House&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The noise in here is deafening. Adventurers from across Kalimdor and
the Eastern Kingdoms crowd the floor, shouting prices, inspecting
strange magical reagents, and trading armor. Several raised platforms
hold the busy auctioneers.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11207
Desc      The auction floor continues deeper into the building.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11203
Desc      The central pillar of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11201 1 11206
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11207
Name     &OAuction House Floor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     More auctioneers stand upon wooden crates here, rapidly fielding bids
from the chaotic crowd of trolls, tauren, orcs, and forsaken. A large
chalkboard tracks the fluctuating prices of copper ore and heavy leather.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11206
Desc      The entrance of the Auction House.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11208
Name     &OValley of Strength - North Walk&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The red dirt path continues to follow the canyon wall. Directly to the
east is a large, inviting wooden structure with smoke billowing from its
chimney—the renowned Broken Tusk inn. To the north, a tunnel leads
deeper into the city.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11219
Desc      A dark tunnel leads toward The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11209
Desc      The entrance to The Broken Tusk inn.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11203
Desc      The central pillar of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11212
Desc      A path winding toward Grommash Hold.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11207 2 11208
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11209
Name     &OThe Broken Tusk - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The smell of roasted meat and strong ale hits you immediately. The Broken
Tusk is a massive, multi-level tavern built of logs and hide. It is the
premier resting spot in Orgrimmar, filled with the loud boasting of
victorious warbands.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11210
Desc      The main bar area.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11208
Desc      The dusty path of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11210
Name     &OThe Broken Tusk - Bar&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive fire pit dominates the center of the room, slowly roasting an
entire boar. Sturdy wooden tables are scattered about, surrounded by
patrons drinking heavily from clay jugs. The innkeeper watches the room
with a hawkish glare.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11209
Desc      The entrance to the inn.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    11211
Desc      A heavy wooden ramp leads to the upper sleeping quarters.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11202 1 11210
  Reset E 1 11202 10 17
Reset M 0 11209 1 11210
  Reset E 1 11203 10 17
Reset O 0 11209 4 11210
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11211
Name     &OThe Broken Tusk - Upper Floor&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The upper floor is surprisingly quiet, insulated by thick kodo hides.
Several hammocks and rough beds are set up here, offering weary
travelers a safe place to rest and recover before heading back out
into the harsh Barrens.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    11210
Desc      The noisy bar is below.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11212
Name     &OValley of Strength - West Walk&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The path winds westward, approaching the most heavily fortified structure
in the Valley. Elite grunts patrol this area with rigorous discipline.
The imposing spires of Grommash Hold rise ominously just to the north.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11213
Desc      The heavily guarded entrance to Grommash Hold.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11208
Desc      The main walk of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11200 2 11212
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11213
Name     &OGrommash Hold - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand at the threshold of Grommash Hold, the seat of power in
Orgrimmar. The architecture here is jagged, aggressive, and built for
war. The air is thick with tension and the smell of ozone from dark
shamanistic rituals.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11214
Desc      The central war room of the Hold.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11212
Desc      The path leading back to the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11200 2 11213
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11214
Name     &OGrommash Hold - War Room&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive tactical map of Kalimdor sits in the center of the room. High
ranking warlords and advisors surround it, arguing over supply lines
and troop movements in Ashenvale. The walls are lined with the weapons
and armor of defeated enemies.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11213
Desc      The entrance to the Hold.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11208 1 11214
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
  Reset E 1 11201 10 12
  Reset E 1 11207 10 5
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11215
Name     &OValley of Strength - East Walk&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The eastern curve of the valley is unbearably hot. The heat radiates
from massive open-air furnaces and anvils located just to the north.
The rhythmic clang of metal striking metal drowns out almost all other
sounds.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11216
Desc      The searing heat of the Forge.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11203
Desc      The central pillar of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11204 3 11215
  Reset E 1 11208 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11216
Name     &RThe Forge&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     Sparks fill the air as the Horde's finest weaponsmiths ply their trade.
Massive iron cauldrons bubble with molten metal. Racks of freshly
forged axes, maces, and thick armor plates line the walls, ready to be
shipped to the front lines.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11215
Desc      The eastern walk of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11205 1 11216
  Reset E 1 11205 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11217
Name     &OValley of Strength - Wyvern Roost Base&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A massive wooden tower rises high into the sky above you. This is the
base of the Orgrimmar Sky Tower, the hub for the city's Wind Riders.
A spiraling wooden ramp wraps around the central pillar, leading up
to the roosts.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11208
Desc      The main walk of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    11218
Desc      The ramp winds upward to the Wyvern Master.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11218
Name     &OOgimmar Sky Tower&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You are high above the Valley of Strength. The wind whips fiercely up
here. Several tame Wind Riders rest on wooden perches, awaiting their
next long-distance flight across the Barrens or beyond. The view of
the city below is spectacular.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    11217
Desc      The ramp winds back down to the dusty valley floor.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11206 2 11218
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11219
Name     &dEntrance to The Drag&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The red dirt gives way to a dark, slightly oppressive tunnel cut straight
through the rock. The light of the sun is blocked out here, replaced by
the eerie glow of shamanistic braziers. This tunnel marks the border
between the Valley of Strength and the shadowy alleys of The Drag.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11220
Desc      The shadowy expanse of The Drag begins here.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11208
Desc      The sunlit Valley of Strength.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11220
Name     &dThe Drag - South Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You step out of the tunnel and into The Drag. Enormous, cured kodo hides
are stretched across the top of the canyon walls, plunging the entire
district into perpetual twilight. The air is thick with the smell of
spices, alchemy, and dark magic.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11221
Desc      The path winds deeper into The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11219
Desc      The tunnel leading back to the Valley of Strength.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11213 2 11220
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11221
Name     &dThe Drag - Main Path&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The dirt path winds between rough-hewn stone buildings and leather tents.
Citizens hurry past, keeping their heads down. To the east, you can hear
the vigorous bubbling of a massive cooking pot and the chopping of meat.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11223
Desc      The path continues north into the shadows.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11222
Desc      The smell of strange stew wafts from the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11220
Desc      The southern entrance of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11218 2 11221
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11222
Name     &OZamja's Cooking Fire&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This open-air alcove is dominated by a massive iron cauldron suspended
over a roaring fire. Spices hang from the rafters, drying in the intense
heat. It is the central hub for learning the culinary arts in Orgrimmar,
though the ingredients are often highly questionable.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11221
Desc      The main path of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11211 1 11222
  Reset E 1 11215 10 16
Reset O 0 11219 1 11222
Reset O 0 11210 2 11222
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11223
Name     &dThe Drag - Shady Corner&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The canyon walls close in tightly here, creating deep, impenetrable
shadows. A fast-talking goblin has set up a small cart here, peddling
goods that glint suspiciously in the dim light.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11225
Desc      The central hub of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11221
Desc      The path leading south.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11224
Desc      A small shop filled with bolts of cloth.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11214 1 11223
  Reset E 1 11216 10 17
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11224
Name     &dMagar's Cloth Goods&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This small shop is surprisingly clean compared to the rest of The Drag.
Bolts of silk, mageweave, and wool are stacked neatly on wooden shelves.
This is where the Horde's spellcasters come to have their robes mended
and tailored.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11223
Desc      The shady corner of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11217 1 11224
Reset O 0 11217 2 11224
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11225
Name     &dThe Drag - Central Walk&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand in the approximate center of The Drag. The overhead canopy of
hides blocks out the sky completely. To the east, the rhythmic scraping
of hide tanning echoes loudly. To the west, a dark, ominous ramp spirals
downward into the earth.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11233
Desc      The path continues north toward the engineering shops.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11226
Desc      The pungent smell of tanning oil comes from the east.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11223
Desc      The shady corner of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11227
Desc      A dark ramp leads down into the Cleft of Shadow.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11213 2 11225
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11226
Name     &OThe Kodohide Leatherworks&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The smell in here is incredibly strong, a mix of salt, blood, and harsh
tanning chemicals. Massive hides from kodos and thunder lizards are
stretched across wooden frames, curing in the dry heat.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11225
Desc      The central walk of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11212 1 11226
  Reset E 1 11215 10 16
Reset O 0 11212 2 11226
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11227
Name     &dEntrance to the Cleft of Shadow&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A wide, spiraling ramp cut directly into the bedrock descends into the
darkness below. Purple and green torches cast long, sickly shadows on
the walls. The air temperature drops noticeably as you stand near the
descent.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11225
Desc      The central walk of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    11228
Desc      The ramp winds down into the subterranean caverns.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11228
Name     &dCleft of Shadow - Descent&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You are walking down the spiraling ramp into the subterranean belly of
Orgrimmar. The noise of the city above fades away, replaced by the
unsettling whispers of demonic entities and the sharp hiss of sharpening
blades.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    11227
Desc      The ramp leads back up to The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    11229
Desc      The ramp bottoms out into a large cavern.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11229
Name     &dCleft of Shadow - Central Cavern&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     You stand in a massive, natural cavern beneath Orgrimmar. Bioluminescent
fungus and fel-green braziers provide the only light. This hidden
sanctuary is where the Horde's warlocks and rogues practice arts deemed
too dangerous or unseemly for the streets above.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11232
Desc      The shadows deepen to the north, favored by the rogues.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11230
Desc      The warlock encampment lies to the south.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    11228
Desc      The ramp leads back to the surface.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11230
Name     &dCleft of Shadow - Warlock Encampment&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     This area hums with chaotic, unstable energy. Books bound in strange
leather are piled haphazardly on stone tables. The warlocks here study
the dark arts, summoning entities from the Twisting Nether to do their
bidding, regardless of the terrible risks.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11229
Desc      The central cavern.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11231
Desc      A summoning circle is etched into the floor to the west.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11210 1 11230
  Reset E 1 11211 10 17
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11231
Name     &dCleft of Shadow - Summoning Circle&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     A massive, intricate rune of power is carved deeply into the stone floor,
glowing with a harsh, fel-green light. The air here tastes like ash and
brimstone. This is where demons are pulled from the void and broken to
the will of the Horde.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11230
Desc      The warlock encampment.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11215 1 11231
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11232
Name     &dCleft of Shadow - Rogue's Corner&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    dark indoors~
Desc     It is incredibly quiet here. The few orcs and trolls present are clad in
dark leather, speaking in hushed whispers or communicating in thieves'
cant. Poisons are mixed, and daggers are honed to razor edges in the
gloom.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11229
Desc      The central cavern.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 11214 1 11232
Reset O 0 11218 1 11232
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11233
Name     &dThe Drag - Northern Path&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     Back on the surface, the path of The Drag continues northward. The air
here is filled with the acrid smell of alchemy and the sharp tang of
black powder. To the east, strange, bubbling sounds emanate from an
apothecary station.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11236
Desc      The path winds deeper into the shadows.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11234
Desc      The entrance to the Apothecarium.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11225
Desc      The central walk of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11234
Name     &dThe Apothecarium&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A localized pocket of the Undercity right here in Orgrimmar. Vials of
glowing liquids, dried herbs, and strange anatomical specimens line the
walls. The Forsaken apothecaries here work tirelessly on new plagues
and potent elixirs.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11233
Desc      The northern path of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11216 1 11234
  Reset E 1 11213 10 17
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11235
Name     &OGoblin Engineering Shop&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This small workshop is a chaotic mess of gears, springs, and black powder.
Explosion marks scorch the walls and ceiling. It is loud, dangerous,
and fully operational. Buy at your own risk.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11236
Desc      The shadowy path outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11219 1 11235
  Reset E 1 11216 10 17
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11236
Name     &dThe Drag - Deep Shadows&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The overhead hides are thickest here, creating an area of almost total
darkness during the day. Sparks flash periodically from the engineering
shop to the west, briefly illuminating the dust motes dancing in the air.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11238
Desc      The path approaches the northern exit.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11233
Desc      The northern path of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11235
Desc      The chaotic Goblin Engineering Shop.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11218 1 11236
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11237
Name     &dTroll Mystic's Hut&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This small hut is adorned with carved wooden masks and shrunken heads.
Incense burns heavily, filling the room with a thick, sweet smoke. This
is a place of voodoo, spirit whispering, and ancient troll magic.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11238
Desc      The path near the northern exit of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 11218 1 11237
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11238
Name     &dThe Drag - North Exit Approach&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The tight, oppressive canyon walls of The Drag finally begin to widen
here. The overhead canopy of hides ends abruptly just to the north,
letting the blinding Durotar sunlight spill onto the red dirt path.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11239
Desc      The path opens up, leading toward the Valley of Honor.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11237
Desc      A small, smoke-filled Troll hut.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11236
Desc      The deep shadows of The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11213 2 11238
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11239
Name     &OPath Toward the Valley of Honor&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You step out from beneath the canopy and blink against the harsh sunlight.
The claustrophobic shadows of The Drag are behind you. The path here
widens significantly, winding its way north toward the martial heart of
the city, the Valley of Honor.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11240
Desc      The path opens into the Valley of Honor.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11238
Desc      The dark entrance back into The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11240
Name     &OValley of Honor - Southern Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The red cliffs of Orgrimmar peel away to reveal a sprawling valley
dedicated to the art of war. Unlike the industrial clatter of the
Valley of Strength, here you hear the rhythmic thrum of drums and
the clash of steel on steel.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11241
Desc      The main path leads toward a large body of water.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11239
Desc      The path leading back toward The Drag.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11223 2 11240
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11241
Name     &OValley of Honor - Water's Edge&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A large, artificial oasis has been created here, fed by subterranean
springs. The water is clear but still, providing a stark contrast to
the dry dust of the valley. A lone troll sits quietly at the edge,
watching a fishing line.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11243
Desc      A path winds around the western shore of the water.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11242
Desc      A dirt path leads to the stables.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11240
Desc      The valley entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11225 1 11241
  Reset E 1 11221 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11242
Name     &OOrgrimmar Stables&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A large, fenced-off area contains several massive kodos and a few
lumbering wolves. The smell of hay and animal musk is thick here.
Stable hands move about, ensuring the Horde's mounts are ready for
the next long patrol.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11241
Desc      The water's edge.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11227 1 11242
Reset M 0 11229 2 11242
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11243
Name     &OValley of Honor - Western Shore&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The path follows the western bank of the valley lake. To the west,
a series of small gardens and huts have been built into the rock,
where the city's herbalists tend to their rare specimens.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11245
Desc      The path continues toward the Hunter's Hall.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11241
Desc      The southern edge of the water.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11244
Desc      The entrance to a vibrant garden hut.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11244
Name     &GThe Garden of the Spirits&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     This small sanctuary is filled with lush greenery and the sweet scent
of blooming herbs. It is meticulously cared for by the Horde's
herbalists, providing the necessary reagents for alchemy and
shamanic rituals.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11243
Desc      The western shore of the lake.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11226 1 11244
Reset O 0 11222 3 11244
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11245
Name     &OValley of Honor - Path to the Hunter's Hall&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The sound of snarling beasts and the whistle of arrows marks your
approach to the Hunter's Hall. A large, open-air structure made of
dark wood and kodo bone stands just to the west.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11247
Desc      The path leads to the northern end of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11243
Desc      The western shore of the lake.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11246
Desc      The entrance to the Hunter's Hall.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11246
Name     &OThe Hunter's Hall&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls are lined with the mounted heads of legendary beasts from
all over Kalimdor. Hunters sit on the floor, cleaning their bows and
feeding their raptors. The air is thick with the smell of musk and
raw meat.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11245
Desc      The path outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11220 1 11246
  Reset E 1 11220 10 16
Reset M 0 11224 2 11246
Reset O 0 11224 5 11246
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11247
Name     &OValley of Honor - Northern Shore&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand at the northern tip of the lake. From here, you have a
clear view of the Ring of Valor to the east—a massive, sunken arena
where the Horde's greatest warriors prove their worth.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11249
Desc      The path leads toward the Ring of Valor.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11245
Desc      The path back toward the Hunter's Hall.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11248
Desc      A path spirals upward to the Hall of the Brave.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11248
Name     &OThe Hall of the Brave&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This massive stone structure is the primary training ground for the
Horde's warriors. The floor is covered in red sand to absorb the
spilled blood of initiates. The air rings with the constant clash
of heavy iron axes.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11247
Desc      The northern shore of the lake.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11221 1 11248
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
Reset M 0 11228 3 11248
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11249
Name     &OPath to the Ring of Valor&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The ground here is heavily trampled by thousands of boots. The
excitement is palpable as you approach the legendary arena. Cheers
and jeers echo from the sunken pit to the east.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11250
Desc      The entrance to the Ring of Valor.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11247
Desc      The northern shore of the lake.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11223 2 11249
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11250
Name     &OThe Ring of Valor - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand at the edge of the Ring of Valor. A massive pit has been
excavated from the red earth, lined with stone seating for the
thousands of spectators who come to watch the combat. 
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11251
Desc      The path continues around the arena.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11249
Desc      The path back toward the lake.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    11252
Desc      A ramp leads down into the combat floor.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11251
Name     &OThe Ring of Valor - Spectator Walk&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The stone walkway circles the upper edge of the arena. Looking down,
you can see the blood-stained sand where countless warriors have
found either glory or death. 
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11250
Desc      The entrance to the arena.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 11229 1 11251
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11252
Name     &OThe Ring of Valor - Combat Floor&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     You stand in the center of the pit. The walls rise high around you,
leaving you with no escape but victory. The sand is coarse and red,
clogging your nostrils with the smell of old copper and sweat.
~
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    11250
Desc      The ramp leads back to the surface.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11228 1 11252
  Reset E 1 11225 10 11
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11253
Name     &OValley of Honor - Eastern Shore&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The path follows the eastern bank of the lake. To the east, several
large, communal huts have been built, their roofs draped with heavy
hides and bones. 
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11255
Desc      The path leads toward the Shamanic dwellings.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11254
Desc      The path winds around the southern end of the lake.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11254
Name     &OValley of Honor - Southern Shore&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You are at the southern curve of the valley lake. The sound of
drums from the Ring of Valor is slightly muted here. To the west,
