~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11253
Desc      The eastern shore.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11241
Desc      The water's edge.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11255
Name     &OValley of Honor - Path to the Spirits&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The air here feels heavy and charged with static. To the east, a
