#ROOM
Vnum     11256
Name     &OThe Shamanic Lodge&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Incense and herbs burn in a central pit, sending sweet-smelling
smoke up into the rafters. Totems representing the four elements
