~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11255
Desc      The path outside.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11222 1 11256
  Reset E 1 11223 10 17
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11257
Name     &OValley of Honor - North Path&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The path winds north, moving away from the lake. The canyon walls
here are sheer and high. To the east, a tunnel has been carved into
the rock, leading toward the Valley of Wisdom.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
