#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11258
Desc      A tunnel leads toward the Valley of Wisdom.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11255
Desc      The path toward the Shamanic Lodge.
~
