#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11258
Name     &dTunnel to the Valley of Wisdom&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A dark, cool tunnel carved straight through the red stone of the
canyon. Torches flicker at regular intervals, casting long shadows.
The bustling noise of the Valley of Honor fades behind you.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11260
Desc      The tunnel opens into the Valley of Wisdom.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11257
Desc      The Valley of Honor.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11259
Name     &OValley of Honor - Northern End&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand at the furthest northern point of the Valley of Honor.
The canyon walls meet here, forming a natural dead end. A few
tattered Horde banners flutter in the wind, marking the borders
of the city's martial district.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11257
Desc      The path leading back toward the lake.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 11228 1 11259
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11260
Name     &WValley of Wisdom - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You step out of the tunnel and into a serene, lush landscape. Green
grass and small pools of water replace the harsh red dust of the other
valleys. Massive wooden elevators hiss as they move people to the upper
plateaus. The air is sweet with the scent of burning herbs.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11258
Desc      The tunnel back to the Valley of Honor.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11261
Desc      The path leads toward the central pool.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11238 1 11260
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11261
Name     &WValley of Wisdom - Central Pool&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     A large, crystal-clear pool sits in the center of the valley, fed by
cascading waterfalls from the cliffs above. Small wooden bridges span
the water, connecting the various Tauren dwellings. 
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11263
Desc      The path continues around the water.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11262
Desc      A small hut sits at the water's edge.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11260
Desc      The valley entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11237 2 11261
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11262
Name     &WShikay's Mystic Hut&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This circular hut is sparsely furnished with woven mats and smooth
stones. Bunches of drying herbs hang from the rafters. It is a place of
quiet contemplation and elemental study.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11261
Desc      The central pool.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11234 1 11262
  Reset E 1 11233 10 16
Reset O 0 11237 3 11262
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11263
Name     &WValley of Wisdom - Northern Path&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The path winds north toward a massive, fortified structure built into
the northern cliff face. To the west, the ground rises toward the base
of a large wooden elevator. 
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11267
Desc      The entrance to Grommash Hold.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11261
Desc      The central pool.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11264
Desc      The path leads to the lower elevator platform.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11239 1 11263
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11264
Name     &WLower Elevator Platform&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand at the base of a marvel of engineering. A massive wooden
platform is suspended by thick, greased chains. A goblin stands nearby,
tinkering with a series of levers and gears.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11263
Desc      The northern path of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    11265
Desc      The elevator platform rises to the upper tier.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11235 1 11264
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11265
Name     &WUpper Elevator Platform&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You are high above the valley floor. From here, you have a stunning
view of the waterfalls and the lush greenery below. The platform creaks
slightly as it settles into place against the upper cliff.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11266
Desc      The path leads to the Tauren delegates.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    11264
Desc      The elevator platform descends to the valley floor.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11266
Name     &WThe Plateau of the Elders&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     This upper plateau is home to the Tauren who represent their people in
Orgrimmar. Several large, colorful tents have been erected here. A
massive bonfire burns in a central pit, surrounded by elders.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11265
Desc      The upper elevator platform.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11232 1 11266
  Reset E 1 11231 10 12
Reset M 0 11236 2 11266
Reset O 0 11239 2 11266
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11267
Name     &OEntrance to Grommash Hold&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The seat of the Warchief is a daunting fortress of iron and wood. Two
Kor'kron Elite Guards stand like statues flanking the massive iron-bound
doors. The air inside is cool and smells of iron and old battles.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11268
Desc      The Hall of the Warchief.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11263
Desc      The northern path of the valley.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11233 2 11267
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11268
Name     &OThe Hall of the Warchief&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This vast hall is the political center of the Horde. Massive banners of
all the Horde races hang from the high ceiling. The Warchief sits upon
his throne at the far end of the room, surrounded by his advisors.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11269
Desc      You approach the throne.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11267
Desc      The entrance of the hold.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11233 2 11268
  Reset E 1 11200 10 16
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11269
Name     &OThrall's Throne&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand at the foot of the throne. Warchief Thrall sits here, his
presence filling the room. To his right stands the veteran Etrigg.
Maps of the world are spread across a nearby table, detailing the
struggles of the Horde across Azeroth.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11268
Desc      The hall leads back to the entrance.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11230 1 11269
  Reset E 1 11230 10 16
Reset M 0 11231 1 11269
Reset O 0 11238 1 11269
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11270
Name     &WValley of Wisdom - Western Shore&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The path follows the western edge of the central pool. The sound of
the crashing waterfalls is deafening here, spraying a fine mist into
the air that keeps the surroundings cool and moist.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11264
Desc      The path to the lower elevator.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11271
Desc      The path winds south.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11271
Name     &WValley of Wisdom - Southwest Corner&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The valley ends here against a sheer red cliff. A small, secluded
grove of trees provides a quiet place for meditation. The water from
the pool laps gently against the shore.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11270
Desc      The western shore of the pool.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11236 1 11271
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11272
Name     &WValley of Wisdom - Eastern Shore&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The path follows the eastern bank of the central water. Several small
Tauren tents are set up along the cliffside, decorated with beads
and feathers. 
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11273
Desc      The path leads toward the waterfalls.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11262
Desc      Shikay's Mystic Hut.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11273
Name     &WValley of Wisdom - Base of the Falls&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     You stand directly beneath a massive waterfall. The power of the falling
water is immense, creating a constant breeze and a shimmering rainbow
in the sunlight. 
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11272
Desc      The eastern shore.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11237 2 11273
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11274
Name     &WThe Spirit Grove&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     A small, hidden grove of ancient trees tucked into a corner of the
valley. The spirits of the elements are strong here, and the air
seems to shimmer with a pale, ethereal light.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11261
Desc      The central pool.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 11237 3 11274
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11275
Name     &WThe Delegate's Tent&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large, communal tent for visiting Tauren dignitaries. It is filled
with comfortable furs and the smell of sweetgrass. Maps and treaties
are piled on a central table.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    11266
Desc      The Plateau of the Elders.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 11232 2 11275
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11276
Name     &OThe Hall of History&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A small room off the side of Grommash Hold dedicated to the history
of the Horde. Tattered banners and ancient weapons are displayed
with great care.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11268
Desc      The Hall of the Warchief.
~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 11235 1 11276
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11277
Name     &OThe War Room - Annex&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A smaller, more private strategy room where Thrall meets with his
closest military advisors. Detailed scouts' reports are pinned to
the walls.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    11268
Desc      The Hall of the Warchief.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11278
Name     &WUpper Plateau - East View&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     Standing at the edge of the upper plateau, you can see across the
entire Valley of Wisdom and even glimpse the rooftops of The Drag
to the south.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    11266
Desc      The Plateau of the Elders.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     11279
Name     &WUpper Plateau - North Edge&d~
Sector   city~
Desc     The very edge of the city. The canyon walls drop off sharply here,
leading out into the untamed wilderness of Durotar.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    11266
Desc      The Plateau of the Elders.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ENDAREA
